HELP SYS_USES_PROJECT_COLLECTION                         Steve Leach, Jan 05

    sys_uses_project_collection( ___dir )

This procedure extends the search list pop_project_search_list with the
directory ___dir.  If ___dir does not exist, it issues a warning.  The
subdirectories of ___dir are assumed to be project directories.

See also:
    HELP *LIB_PROJECT
    HELP *POP_PROJECT_SEARCH_LIST
    HELP *SYS_USES_PROJECT
    HELP *USES_PROJECT
